visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Oldenburg

designer: Nicole Fally

approved: true
description: <p>Oldenburg is inspired by nearly \
  monoline handwritting seen on a series of German \
  posters. It has been changed and adaped to be more \
  broadly useful design than a more faithful \
  interpretation would have been. Despite the \
  increased ulity in Oldernburg it still presenst \
  plenty of the whimsical feeling that made its \
  source so attractive. Oldenburg can be used a in \
  a wide range of sizes.</p>

font.Oldenburg-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Oldenburg-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

